类 Code.Chain

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.tools.javac.v8.code.Code.Chain
包容类：
Code
public static class Code.Chain
extends java.lang.Object

A chain represents a list of unresolved jumps. Jump locations are sorted in decreasing order.

字段摘要
 Bits defined
          The set of variables alive at the jump.
 Code.Chain next
          The next jump in the list.
 int pc
          The position of the jump instruction.
 int stacksize
          The stacksize after the jump instruction.
 
构造方法摘要
Code.Chain(int pc, int stacksize, Code.Chain next, Bits defined)
          Construct a chain from its jump position, stacksize, previous chain, and set of defined variables.
